001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.currentStatus.AlarmStatusResponse;
007
008import java.math.BigInteger;
009
010@HistoryLogProps(
011    opCode = 5,
012    displayName = "Alarm Activated",
013    internalName = "LID_ALARM_ACTIVATED",
014    usedByTidepool = true
015)
016public class AlarmActivatedHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
017    
018    private long alarmId;
019    
020    public AlarmActivatedHistoryLog() {}
021    public AlarmActivatedHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, long alarmId) {
022        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
023        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, alarmId);
024        this.alarmId = alarmId;
025        
026    }
027
028    public AlarmActivatedHistoryLog(long alarmId) {
029        this(0, 0, alarmId);
030    }
031
032    public int typeId() {
033        return 5;
034    }
035
036    /**
037     * <table border="1">
038     * <caption>Parsed fields for AlarmActivatedHistoryLog:</caption>
039     * <tr><td><code>alarmId</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
040     * </table>
041     */
042    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
043        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
044        this.cargo = raw;
045        parseBase(raw);
046        this.alarmId = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 10);
047        
048    }
049
050    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, long alarmId) {
051        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
052            new byte[]{5, 0},
053            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
054            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
055            Bytes.toUint32(alarmId)));
056    }
057    public long getAlarmId() {
058        return alarmId;
059    }
060
061    /**
062     * @return the type of alarm
063     */
064    public AlarmStatusResponse.AlarmResponseType getAlarmResponseType() {
065        return AlarmStatusResponse.AlarmResponseType.fromSingularId(alarmId);
066    }
067}
